{"article_id":"xGokfPL5RhnEbEKg","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"Florida Sen. Marco Rubio on Sunday touted his debate performance , amid criticism about \" scripted \" responses and him needing to repeat his opposition to President Obama","depth":3},{"id":1,"text":"to defend a sustained attack by GOP presidential rival Chris Christie .","depth":3},{"id":2,"text":"Christie , the governor of New Jersey , argued during the Saturday night debate","depth":5},{"id":3,"text":"that Rubio would be like Obama","depth":7},{"id":4,"text":"if elected","depth":7},{"id":5,"text":"-- a freshman senator","depth":8},{"id":6,"text":"leading the country","depth":8},{"id":7,"text":"with essentially no experience","depth":8},{"id":8,"text":"running a government .","depth":8},{"id":9,"text":"Rubio said several times during the attack","depth":6},{"id":10,"text":"that Obama indeed \" knows exactly what he 's doing , ''","depth":7},{"id":11,"text":"which is trying to make the country \" like the rest of the world . \"","depth":7},{"id":12,"text":"\" I would pay them to keep running that clip","depth":8},{"id":13,"text":"because that 's what I believe passionately , \"","depth":8},{"id":14,"text":"he said on ABC 's `` This Week . ''","depth":7},{"id":15,"text":"\" It 's one of the reasons","depth":8},{"id":16,"text":"why I 'm not running for re-election to the Senate","depth":8},{"id":17,"text":"and I 'm running for president . ''","depth":7},{"id":18,"text":"In the debate exchange , Rubio also said","depth":6},{"id":19,"text":"that Christie could barely pull himself off the campaign trail","depth":7},{"id":20,"text":"to return to New Jersey","depth":8},{"id":21,"text":"to deal with last month ' s blizzard .","depth":8},{"id":22,"text":"\" They had to shame you into going back , \"","depth":9},{"id":23,"text":"Rubio said .","depth":9},{"id":24,"text":"\" You stayed there for 36 hours .","depth":8},{"id":25,"text":"And then he left","depth":8},{"id":26,"text":"and came back to campaign .","depth":8},{"id":27,"text":"Those are the facts . \"","depth":6},{"id":28,"text":"Christie , a former federal prosecutor , accused Rubio of distorting the facts about his governorship ,","depth":6},{"id":29,"text":"including some about the state ' s financial problems .","depth":6},{"id":30,"text":"\" That 's what Washington , D.C. , does","depth":8},{"id":31,"text":"-- the drive-by shot at the beginning with incorrect and incomplete information and then the memorized 25-second speech .","depth":8},{"id":32,"text":"That is exactly what his advisers gave him , \"","depth":7},{"id":33,"text":"said Christie ,","depth":7},{"id":34,"text":"who repeated a version of that response several times","depth":8},{"id":35,"text":"as Rubio continued .","depth":8},{"id":36,"text":"Rubio is now in the top tier of GOP White House candidates with billionaire businessman Donald Trump and Texas Sen. Ted Cruz .","depth":3},{"id":37,"text":"His recent rise has resulted in efforts by those in the GOP field ,","depth":5},{"id":38,"text":"including Christie ,","depth":5},{"id":39,"text":"to slow his momentum .","depth":4},{"id":40,"text":"As a Republican governor","depth":6},{"id":41,"text":"leading a Democratic-leaning state ,","depth":6},{"id":42,"text":"Christie hopes to appeal to independent-minded New Hampshire voters in the state primary Tuesday","depth":5},{"id":43,"text":"to keep his campaign alive .","depth":4},{"id":44,"text":"He accused Rubio of scripted responses in the days","depth":5},{"id":45,"text":"leading up to the debate , too .","depth":5},{"id":46,"text":"Rubio also argued Sunday , as proof","depth":7},{"id":47,"text":"his debate remarks resonated with supporters ,","depth":7},{"id":48,"text":"that his campaign raised more money in the first hour of the debate than in any other debate .","depth":6},{"id":49,"text":"\" As far as that message , I hope","depth":9},{"id":50,"text":"they keep running it .","depth":9},{"id":51,"text":"And I 'm going to keep saying","depth":9},{"id":52,"text":"because it 's true , ''","depth":9},{"id":53,"text":"he said .","depth":7},{"id":54,"text":"`` Barack Obama ... said","depth":8},{"id":55,"text":"he wanted to change the country .","depth":8},{"id":56,"text":"He 's doing it in a way","depth":8},{"id":57,"text":"that is robbing us of everything","depth":9},{"id":58,"text":"that is special . \"","depth":9}],"relations":[{"parent":117,"left":94,"right":116,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":94,"left":60,"right":93,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":60,"left":0,"right":1,"relation":"purpose","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":93,"left":75,"right":92,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":75,"left":66,"right":74,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":66,"left":2,"right":65,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":65,"left":61,"right":64,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":61,"left":3,"right":4,"relation":"condition","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":64,"left":62,"right":63,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":62,"left":5,"right":6,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":63,"left":7,"right":8,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":74,"left":68,"right":73,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":68,"left":9,"right":67,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":67,"left":10,"right":11,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":73,"left":70,"right":72,"relation":"evaluation","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":70,"left":69,"right":14,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":69,"left":12,"right":13,"relation":"explanation","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":72,"left":71,"right":17,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":71,"left":15,"right":16,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":92,"left":84,"right":91,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":84,"left":78,"right":83,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"pare